OL,8,     Gorganised the event down to the
OL,9,     Glast sugar lump. Events take a
OL,10,     Gsudden turn.
OL,11,G0105FGareth Edwards's Great Welsh
OL,12,     FAdventure
OL,13,     GIt's a scorcher as Gareth Edwards
